In [17]:
# Extraction des couples de variables ayant une corrlation suprieure  0.8
corr_threshold = 0.8
corr_pairs = {}

for col in corr_matrix.columns:
    corr_pairs[col] = []
    corr_values = corr_matrix[abs(corr_matrix[col]) > corr_threshold][col].index.tolist()
    for pair in corr_values:
        if pair != col:
            corr_pairs[col].append(pair)

# Affichage des couples de variables ayant une corrlation suprieure  0.8
print("Couples de variables ayant une corrlation suprieure  0.8 :\n")
for col, pairs in corr_pairs.items():
    if len(pairs) > 0:
        for pair in pairs:
            print(col, "-", pair)

Couples de variables ayant une corrlation suprieure  0.8 :

infant deaths - under-five deaths 
percentage expenditure - GDP
under-five deaths  - infant deaths
GDP - percentage expenditure
 thinness  1-19 years -  thinness 5-9 years
 thinness 5-9 years -  thinness  1-19 years
